		<div class="headline-container">
			<h1 class="article-hed">
				Good Leadership Is About Communicating “Why”
			</h1>
		</div>

<div class="article-dek-group">
	<div class="article-dek">It’s easy to get bogged down in “what” and “how.”
		<div class="article-byline ">
			<span class="by-prefix">by </span>
			<ul class="article-byline-list">
					<li class="article-author"><a href="/search?term=nancy%20duarte">Nancy Duarte</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

		<div class="article-byline detached">
			<span class="by-prefix">by </span>
			<ul class="article-byline-list">
